author: USA TODAY, Ken Alltucker, USA TODAY
title: Labs are testing 100,000 people each day for the coronavirus. That's still not enough.
description: Public and private labs now complete more than 100,000 COVID-19 tests each day. Still, many are denied tests and labs struggle with a growing backlog.
content:
